  "remarks": "\nBahmanyar Morteza BAHMANYAR is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. Bahmanyar Morteza BAHMANYAR is or has been providing support for or facilitating the development of a nuclear weapon delivery system in, or for use in, Iran.",
